{"tid":696452,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"新元氣高速線究竟係乜嘢原理","createTime":"2018-06-10T06:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T12:56:18.000Z","uid":42884,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"adaec52cccd003115332b962527739a4e44eaee6","tid":696452,"uid":42884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:19:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人知新嘅元氣高速線（好似片中呢一間）列車嘅運作原理係咩？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LOod4MuIGdc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLOod4MuIGdc&d=8rve7%2FShRofpxQpRRLTjDzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f2283e3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LOod4MuIGdc</a><br />\n<br />\n根據平時去食嘅觀察，新版嘅元氣高速線有以下特點<br />\n- 每一架列車有兩卡<br />\n- 兩卡以間係冇實體的連接<br />\n- 如果用手嘗試分開兩卡，感覺佢哋係用磁力連結<br />\n- 試過百厭，大力分開兩卡車。分開左之後，後面嗰卡係會唔識番廚房，要店員攞番入去。睇落嗰車冇摩打<br />\n- 列車駛嚟嘅時間，中間凸出嗰個路軌裡面係有沙沙聲發出<br />\n- 有轉彎位嘅話，列車會減速，轉完彎會加番速<br />\n<br />\n究竟有冇人知成個元氣高速線嘅運作原理係乜嘢？？<br />\n係咪凸出嗰舊野下面係磁石，根據送餐目的地，郁舊車去到目的地？<br />\n攞完野食㩒制，下面舊磁石就牽引列車番廚房<br />\n<br />\n成日好想攞起架車嚟睇，但又驚畀店員話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d834903370a180e0663609d6d0f2109df37b24","tid":696452,"uid":141871,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:20:48.000Z","msg":"食野你就食野啦<br />\n搞咁多野做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432ed72a553a0af1497c6e78282512233c09e649","tid":696452,"uid":29914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"唔好咁撚仆街啦，要研究就自己搵資料啦。"},{"pid":"0e1106209744e737cb051d4bad7ec7c1ce95f219","tid":696452,"uid":151664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:31:57.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩 使唔使成間鋪拆埋你睇？？"},{"pid":"5fd66ee11c5d19d06a38e3bc2229f52cfe0c99d5","tid":696452,"uid":42884,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:33:57.000Z","msg":"做人正常都有好奇心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffcf26c08e9e0c102a1a40cefff511dd4a954ece","tid":696452,"uid":2772,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5fd66ee11c5d19d06a38e3bc2229f52cfe0c99d5","tid":696452,"uid":42884,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:33:57.000Z","msg":"做人正常都有好奇心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"正常人唔會亂攪人d野囉<br />\n<br />\n唔知你受咩教育大"},{"pid":"ca154239f765d5cec19c4df869c8c3dcfc196269","tid":696452,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:56:18.000Z","msg":"Linear motor?"}]}